+# 2048 in C
+
+A portable console implementation of the 2048 game written in C.
+
+## Build
+
+Using Make:
+
+```sh
+make
+```
+
+Or compile directly:
+
+```sh
+gcc -std=c11 -O2 -Wall -Wextra -pedantic src/main.c -o 2048
+```
+
+## Run
+
+```sh
+./2048
+```
+
+On Windows PowerShell, run:
+
+```powershell
+.\2048.exe
+```
+
+## Controls
+
+- `W`, `A`, `S`, `D` to move
+- `R` to restart
+- `Q` to quit
